QuestData.Title: The Siege Swells
QuestData.Description: Today's mantid swarm is among the worst I've seen. We are lucky to have Niuzao join us in battle.$b$bHelp him, $c. Return to the courtyard, and join in the defense of our temple.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat 25 Sra'thik attackers at Niuzao Temple.
